      <title>哥伦比亚 Petro 寻求达成协议，让 Ecopetrol 生产委内瑞拉石油和天然气</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/colombian-leader-seeks-deal-to-let-ecopetrol-produce-venezuelan-oil-and-gas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗在访问加拉加斯后表示，哥伦比亚正在制定一项在委内瑞拉生产石油和天然气的协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/colombian-leader-seeks-deal-to-let-ecopetrol-produce-venezuelan-oil-and-gas</guid>
